              "id": "21da1ebb",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2 data-start=\"63\" data-end=\"238\">Midland Floor Care serves commercial clients across the DMV</h2><p data-start=\"63\" data-end=\"238\">With fast, professional floor care and facility services. Same day or next day options are available in most areas.</p><p data-start=\"240\" data-end=\"254\"><strong data-start=\"240\" data-end=\"254\">What we do</strong></p><ul data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"539\"><li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"285\"><p data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"285\">Commercial carpet cleaning</p></li><li data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"325\"><p data-start=\"288\" data-end=\"325\">Tile and grout cleaning and sealing</p></li><li data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"370\"><p data-start=\"328\" data-end=\"370\">Hard surface restoration and maintenance</p></li><li data-start=\"371\" data-end=\"420\"><p data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"420\">Polished concrete (prep, stain, polish, seal)</p></li><li data-start=\"421\" data-end=\"456\"><p data-start=\"423\" data-end=\"456\">Upholstery and leather cleaning</p></li><li data-start=\"457\" data-end=\"507\"><p data-start=\"459\" data-end=\"507\">Janitorial and housekeeping for select clients</p></li><li data-start=\"508\" data-end=\"539\"><p data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"539\">Last-minute and event support</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"558\"><strong data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"558\">Where we work</strong></p><p data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"719\"><strong data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"578\">Washington, DC</strong><br data-start=\"578\" data-end=\"581\" />Downtown, Capitol Hill, Navy Yard, NoMa, Dupont Circle, Georgetown, Foggy Bottom, Shaw, U Street, Capitol Riverfront, Southwest Waterfront</p><p data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"1078\"><strong data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"733\">Maryland</strong><br data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"736\" />Montgomery County: Bethesda, Chevy Chase, Silver Spring, Rockville, Gaithersburg, Germantown<br data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"831\" />Prince George\u2019s County: Hyattsville, College Park, Greenbelt, Largo, Bowie, National Harbor<br data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"925\" />Howard County: Columbia, Ellicott City<br data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"966\" />Anne Arundel County: Annapolis, Glen Burnie, Hanover<br data-start=\"1018\" data-end=\"1021\" />Frederick and surrounding business corridors (by request)</p><p data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1347\"><strong data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1101\">Northern Virginia</strong><br data-start=\"1101\" data-end=\"1104\" />Arlington: Rosslyn, Crystal City, Pentagon City<br data-start=\"1151\" data-end=\"1154\" />City of Alexandria<br data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1175\" />Fairfax County: Tysons, McLean, Reston, Herndon, Fairfax, Springfield, Annandale<br data-start=\"1255\" data-end=\"1258\" />Loudoun County: Ashburn, Sterling, Leesburg<br data-start=\"1301\" data-end=\"1304\" />Prince William County: Woodbridge, Manassas</p><p data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1374\"><strong data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1374\">Industries we support</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1628\"><li data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1413\"><p data-start=\"1377\" data-end=\"1413\">Corporate offices and headquarters</p></li><li data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1447\"><p data-start=\"1416\" data-end=\"1447\">Hotels and hospitality venues</p></li><li data-start=\"1448\" data-end=\"1479\"><p data-start=\"1450\" data-end=\"1479\">Retail and shopping centers</p></li><li data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1517\"><p data-start=\"1482\" data-end=\"1517\">Healthcare and medical facilities</p></li><li data-start=\"1518\" data-end=\"1546\"><p data-start=\"1520\" data-end=\"1546\">Schools and universities</p></li><li data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1585\"><p data-start=\"1549\" data-end=\"1585\">Government and municipal buildings</p></li><li data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1628\"><p data-start=\"1588\" data-end=\"1628\">Restaurants, breweries, and food service</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1646\"><strong data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1646\">Availability:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1647\" data-end=\"1842\"><li data-start=\"1647\" data-end=\"1698\"><p data-start=\"1649\" data-end=\"1698\">Priority dispatch for active commercial clients</p></li><li data-start=\"1699\" data-end=\"1744\"><p data-start=\"1701\" data-end=\"1744\">Nights, weekends, and off-peak scheduling</p></li><li data-start=\"1745\" data-end=\"1802\"><p data-start=\"1747\" data-end=\"1802\">Same day or next day for most DC and close-in suburbs</p></li><li data-start=\"1803\" data-end=\"1842\"><p data-start=\"1805\" data-end=\"1842\">Multi-site programs across the region</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1868\"><strong data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1868\">How scheduling works</strong></p><ol data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"2054\"><li data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"1924\"><p data-start=\"1872\" data-end=\"1924\">Quick call or message with your scope and timeline</p></li><li data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1962\"><p data-start=\"1928\" data-end=\"1962\">On-site walkthrough and estimate</p></li><li data-start=\"1963\" data-end=\"2010\"><p data-start=\"1966\" data-end=\"2010\">Service scheduled to match your operations</p></li><li data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2054\"><p data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2054\">Follow up and maintenance plan if needed</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2227\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\"><strong data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2085\">Schedule an on-site visit</strong></a><br data-start=\"2085\" data-end=\"2088\" />Ready to book. Call us or request an on-site visit, and we\u2019ll walk the space, confirm scope, and deliver a clear plan, price, and timeline.</p><ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/the-top-methods-for-cost-effective-floor-maintenance/\">The Top Methods for Cost-Effective Floor Maintenance</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li>\n</ul>",
